name: Mad Scientist Panda - KuD-052
description: He is to smart, way to smart for a panda and thirst for knowledge. So thirst for it which made him crazy, doing anything for knowledge. He want to know the reason for anything and want to make something new that never exist in the world. He is experimenting on everything including on his race as well, making cyborg or even zombies like frankenstein. He can raise the dead with science!
